summary: WAMFACTURING CENTER: 20,000 LED lights, 100 HEN’ SP: 1040. PRODUCT CODE-1040: ‘Phenomenon of the ‘WACHINE TYPE, the product code is: “Wachine Type”. The productcode is a combination of ’Wacheine, a type of tape, and a tape measure. It is used to measure tape length, tape weight and glue application.
